      Nixle keeps you up-to-date with relevant information from your community. In six months, I led the product, UX, interface, information architecture, and front-end development on both web and iOS platforms for <a href="http://nixle.com"target="_blank">Nixle</a>, which keeps you up-to-date with relevant information from your community.
%section.project-body
